data.description: Beautiful Spacious Detached Townhome, 3331 QF FT, smooth stucco Spanish Home, Venetian Ceilings 5 Bedrooms 4 Bathrooms One bedroom converted to a Formal Office, Attached 3 car Garage, One car space in driveway, Gated Driveway, Private Backyard with Patio & Gated on both sides, Beautiful Landscape all around, Vincent Park Across the street & Redondo Union High, Blocks Away from Jr High & Elementary School, Two Master Bedrooms with Large Balcony with two beautiful large fans, one bedroom with a Romeo and Juliet Balcony, Huge Master Bedroom w/ Fireplace, Vaulted Ceilings w/ Long hallway with His & Hers closet, large walk in shower, His & Hers Sink, Soaking Large jetted tub, Private Water Closet, Private Large Covered Master balcony, Grand Entry, Chandelier with Spiral wood Staircase & large upper Foyer, Open Large Living room w/ Granite floors, Formal Dining, Dual Living Area & Huge Fireplace, Beautiful Large & tall Kitchen Island, Open Kitchen floor, One Bedroom on Bottom floor With Large Walk-in closet With French Doors to back yard, Central Heating & A/C, Laundry Room on second floor With W/D Hookups, Two Bedrooms have new carpet. MUST SEE TO APPRECIATE!  4 blocks from the Beach,   Home comes with WaterBoy System
